snippet.title: 10 Celebrities Who Defended Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard...
snippet.description:
10 Celebrities Who Defended Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard
When it comes to the case between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, it’d be VERY easy to go and say that Amber Heard is winning due to Depp’s lose of both the Libel case and the appeal that was to follow. And while he has made headway, many note that he’s losing a lot of ground despite the evidence he has that. You might even think that he’s a bit alone out there in the world, but he’s honestly not. Because many people have stood up for him and defended him against Amber Heard. Allow us to show you them.

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the people who have stepped forward to talk about Johnny Depp and how he isn’t what Amber Heard paints him as. Were you shocked by some of the big names that came forward to help Johnny Depp? Which ones words made you feel good knowing that Johnny is likely innocent of what he’s been charged of? Is there someone else you feel can go and step up to help Depp? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we’ll see you next time on the channel!
